high_descs: Turn left to the counter.
Pick up the lotion bottle to the left of the sink.
Turn left and go to the toilet.
Put the lotion bottle on the back of the toilet.
Go right to the sink.
Pick up the lotion bottle in the cabinet below the sink.
Go back to the toilet.
Put the lotion bottle on the back of the toilet to the left of the spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put two lotion bottles on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: cross the bathroom to the vanity
pick up the soap bottle sitting on the vanity beside the sink
cross over to the toilet
set the soap bottle on the back of the toilet
go back to the vanity and open the cabinet underneath it
take out a soap bottle from the cabinet
go back to the toilet
set the soap bottle on the back of the toilet with the other soap bottle
anns.task_desc: move both soap bottles to the back of the toilet

high_descs: Turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the soap on the counter.
Go to the toilet to your left.
Put the soap on the back of the toilet.
Turn right and move forward, then turn left to face the sink counter.
Open the leftmost cabinet under the sink counter and take out the soap from inside.
Go to the toilet to your left.
Put the soap on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put two soaps on the back of the toilet.
